# Graph UI agent

- Use `@xyflow/react` v12; import `@xyflow/react/dist/style.css` only in graph entry components.
- Custom nodes: `course` → NodeCard, `career` → CareerNode.
- Convert seed/DB nodes via `lib/flow.ts`; do not duplicate mapping logic in pages.
- Keep canvas positions from seed JSON unless adding an explicit auto-layout feature.
